"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16p=
x;">But the trend is clear: answers to even very hard questions are becomin=
g cheaper and cheaper and cheaper. Which means the ability to ask them is g=
