0;Don&#8217;t worry, everybody will be fine.&#8221;</p><p style=3D"margin: =
0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">The s=
ituation, like most situations, is dynamic. Dynamic situations require stra=
tegy.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height:=
 26px;font-size: 16px;">If our highest and best use isn&#8217;t our ability=
