4, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">When I started writing this =
piece, I didn&#8217;t know it was going to end up where it ended up. It sta=
rted as a normal strategy essay.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: r=
gb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">I had six strategies com=
panies have historically used for dealing with commoditization at one layer=
 of the stack &#8211; similar to those in the One Strategy section &#8211; =
and that was pretty much going to be the payload.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 =
0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">The ide=
