>, and </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/107139b3-c287-48f1-b=
3ff-934c900e8b55?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m=
