color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">Then last week, =
something interesting started happening.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;=
color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">On Friday, I cam=
e into the office, meditated, and then had the insight at the beginning of =
this piece: niti niti economics.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: r=
gb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>On Saturday, on my=
